snippet.title: Anthony Hamilton - Charlene (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Anthony Hamilton's official music video for 'Charlene'. Click to listen to Anthony Hamilton on Spotify: http://smarturl.it/AHSpot?IQid=AnthonyHCHA

As featured on Comin' From Where I'm From. Click to buy the track via iTunes: http://smarturl.it/AHCFWITunes?IQid=AnthonyHCHA

Subscribe to Anthony Hamilton on YouTube: http://smarturl.it/AHSub?IQid=AnthonyHCHA

Lyrics:

Baby I'll be
Sitting here waiting on you to come home again
I won't leave
Promise I'll be here to the very end
By your side
To protect you and to love you and to be with you for life
Come on home to me Charlene
